txt.en: 'Nevid, kill the duvodiad!'
'Enough! Stop this foolishness!'
'Guards, what are you waiting for!'
Defeated Madin Brenin and his guards
'Curse you, Duvodiad! Murderer! You will die!'
Defeated Madin Brenin and his guards
Munfaeril has asked you to take a warning to Madin, Brenin of Barnavon.

'Ha! You dare threaten the Brenin of Barnavon? I have the protection of Saruman the Wise... you have no authority here.

'Oh-ho! You present me with the Sigil of the Uch-gwirod and expect me to believe the spirit herself sent you? How do I know you did not steal it from the shrine? For that alone you should die.

'Indeed, your interference and blasphemy will not be brooked, duvodiad. Prepare to join the spirits. Guards!'
Deliver Munfaeril's warning to Madin Brenin in Barnavon.
'Murderer! Begone from this place and never return, else you will be killed.'
Defeat Madin Brenin and his guards.
Defeat Madin Brenin and his guards.
'My son is a fool...I will deal with you myself!'
Deliver Munfaeril's warning to Madin Brenin
'You will die before the day is out, Duvodiad...I swear it!'
